The Post Office authorities have documentary evidence in Deighan's own handwriting, that certain letters were received in the mails at his office, which letters the parties to whom they were addressed say they never received. Deighan was taken to Toledo today in charge of a United States Marshal for a hearing.

abstract: After nightfall wild ducks infest the grain fields in the vicinity of Putah Creek, Alameda County, in great numbers. They have nearly devastated 400 acres on the Curry farm. It is thought by her physician that she cannot live until morning.

abstract: CHICAGO, Feb. 25.--The death of Judge Bently B. Benedict, of Rapid City, Dakota, which occurred very suddenly at Rock Island yesterday, excited such suspicious that an inquest was held today.
